column14:
'desc': [u'

Littles Maxi Feeder Cover (Multicolor) Price: Rs.75

Babies are constantly in a stage of growth and development and need to be pampered and taken care of to turn them into well-grown individuals. The Maxi Feeder Cover from Littles provides you with a protecting cover for your baby’s feeding bottle in order to maintain its temperature.

The Littles Maxi Feeder Cover boasts of an Animal Theme on the outside and is insulated for extra protection. This Medium-Sized Feeder Cover from Littles is Durable and Easy to Clean so that using it on a daily basis does not prove to be a hassle. The Built-In Strap allows you to carry the bottle around conveniently. The dimensions of this Little Maxi Feeder Cover are 5.2 x 7.4 x 21.4 cm and can be used for both girls and boys.

']
